# Raw client-named field reports — adopters / agents drop these in-tree, but
# the repo is heading public. They MUST be sanitized into a target-agnostic
# docs/adoption-report-*.md before anything is committed. The raw form is
# never tracked. (Hygiene: cf. docs/first-consumer-asks.md round-10/11.)
FIELD-REPORT-*.md
*-field-report.md
